			<h4><a id="comment_link_64120259" name="comment_link_64120259" href="//it.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23177939&amp;cid=64120259" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64120259)" >Beware the lying "news"</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64120259" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64120259); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>3</a>)</span></h4>
